{"1":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","c":"إِذَا","d":"idhā","e":"When"},{"b":"0.61","c":"جَاءَكَ","d":"jāaka","e":"come to you"},{"b":"2.8","c":"الْمُنَافِقُونَ","d":"l-munāfiqūna","e":"the hypocrites"},{"b":"4.5","c":"قَالُوا","d":"qālū","e":"they say"},{"b":"5.4","c":"نَشْهَدُ","d":"nashhadu","e":"We testify"},{"b":"6.2","c":"إِنَّكَ","d":"innaka","e":"that you"},{"b":"7.7","c":"لَرَسُولُ","d":"larasūlu","e":"(are) surely (the) Messenger"},{"b":"8.9","c":"اللَّهِ","d":"l-lahi","e":"(of) Allah"},{"b":"9.5","c":"وَاللَّهُ","d":"wal-lahu","e":"And Allah"},{"b":"10.6","c":"يَعْلَمُ","d":"yaʿlamu","e":"knows"},{"b":"11.4","c":"إِنَّكَ","d":"innaka","e":"that you"},{"b":"12.7","c":"لَرَسُولُهُ","d":"larasūluhu","e":"(are) surely His Messenger"},{"b":"14.2","c":"وَاللَّهُ","d":"wal-lahu","e":"and Allah"},{"b":"15.2","c":"يَشْهَدُ","d":"yashhadu","e":"testifies"},{"b":"16.","c":"إِنَّ","d":"inna","e":"that"},{"b":"17.4","c":"الْمُنَافِقِينَ","d":"l-munāfiqīna","e":"the hypocrites"},{"b":"19.1","c":"لَكَاذِبُونَ","d":"lakādhibūna","e":"(are) surely liars"}],"a":{"g":"When the hypocrites come to you, [O Muhammad], they say, \"We testify that you are the Messenger of Allah.\" And Allah knows that you are His Messenger, and Allah testifies that the hypocrites are liars."}},"2":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","c":"اتَّخَذُوا","d":"ittakhadhū","e":"They take"},{"b":"2.4","c":"أَيْمَانَهُمْ","d":"aymānahum","e":"their oaths"},{"b":"3.8","c":"جُنَّةً","d":"junnatan","e":"(as) a cover"},{"b":"6.4","c":"فَصَدُّوا","d":"faṣaddū","e":"so they turn away"},{"b":"7.4","c":"عَنْ","d":"ʿan","e":"from"},{"b":"8.5","c":"سَبِيلِ","d":"sabīli","e":"(the) Way"},{"b":"9.4","c":"اللَّهِ","d":"l-lahi","e":"(of) Allah"},{"b":"12.3","c":"إِنَّهُمْ","d":"innahum","e":"Indeed"},{"b":"14.1","c":"سَاءَ","d":"sāa","e":"evil is"},{"b":"16.3","c":"مَا","d":"mā","e":"what"},{"b":"16.6","c":"كَانُوا","d":"kānū","e":"they used (to)"},{"b":"17.6","c":"يَعْمَلُونَ","d":"yaʿmalūna","e":"do"}],"a":{"g":"They have taken their oaths as a cover, so they averted [people] from the way of Allah. Indeed, it was evil that they were doing."}},"3":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","c":"ذَلِكَ","d":"dhālika","e":"That"},{"b":"0.85","c":"بِأَنَّهُمْ","d":"bi-annahum","e":"(is) because"},{"b":"3.0","c":"ءَامَنُوا","d":"āmanū","e":"they believed"},{"b":"4.0","c":"ثُمَّ","d":"thumma","e":"then"},{"b":"5.3","c":"كَفَرُوا","d":"kafarū","e":"they disbelieved;"},{"b":"6.1","c":"فَطُبِعَ","d":"faṭubiʿa","e":"so were sealed"},{"b":"6.9","c":"عَلَى","d":"ʿalā","e":"[upon]"},{"b":"7.6","c":"قُلُوبِهِمْ","d":"qulūbihim","e":"their hearts"},{"b":"8.8","c":"فَهُمْ","d":"fahum","e":"so they"},{"b":"9.5","c":"لَا","d":"lā","e":"(do) not"},{"b":"9.9","c":"يَفْقَهُونَ","d":"yafqahūna","e":"understand"}],"a":{"g":"That is because they believed, and then they disbelieved; so their hearts were sealed over, and they do not understand."}},"4":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","c":"وَإِذَا","d":"wa-idhā","e":"And when"},{"b":"0.77","c":"رَأَيْتَهُمْ","d":"ra-aytahum","e":"you see them"},{"b":"2.0","c":"تُعْجِبُكَ","d":"tuʿ'jibuka","e":"pleases you"},{"b":"3.1","c":"أَجْسَامُهُمْ","d":"ajsāmuhum","e":"their bodies"},{"b":"5","c":"وَإِنْ","d":"wa-in","e":"and if"},{"b":"6.1","c":"يَقُولُوا","d":"yaqūlū","e":"they speak"},{"b":"7.0","c":"تَسْمَعْ","d":"tasmaʿ","e":"you listen"},{"b":"7.8","c":"لِقَوْلِهِمْ","d":"liqawlihim","e":"to their speech"},{"b":"9.5","c":"كَأَنَّهُمْ","d":"ka-annahum","e":"as if they (were)"},{"b":"11.1","c":"خُشُبٌ","d":"khushubun","e":"pieces of wood"},{"b":"12.6","c":"مُسَنَّدَةٌ","d":"musannadatun","e":"propped up"},{"b":"15.0","c":"يَحْسَبُونَ","d":"yaḥsabūna","e":"They think"},{"b":"16.2","c":"كُلَّ","d":"kulla","e":"every"},{"b":"16.8","c":"صَيْحَةٍ","d":"ṣayḥatin","e":"shout"},{"b":"17.8","c":"عَلَيْهِمْ","d":"ʿalayhim","e":"(is) against them"},{"b":"19.3","c":"هُمُ","d":"humu","e":"They"},{"b":"19.7","c":"الْعَدُوُّ","d":"l-ʿaduwu","e":"(are) the enemy"},{"b":"20.7","c":"فَاحْذَرْهُمْ","d":"fa-iḥ'dharhum","e":"so beware of them"},{"b":"2