 the ones who say, \"Do not spend on those who are with the Messenger of Allah until they disband.\" And to Allah belongs the depositories of the heavens and the earth, but the hypocrites do not understand."}},"8":{"w":[{"b":"0.05","c":"يَقُولُونَ","d":"yaqūlūna","e":"They say"},{"b":"1.3","c":"لَئِنْ","d":"la-in","e":"If"},{"b":"1.6","c":"رَجَعْنَا","d":"rajaʿnā","e":"we return"},{"b":"4.4","c":"إِلَى","d":"ilā","e":"to"},{"b":"4.8","c":"الْمَدِينَةِ","d":"l-madīnati","e":"Al-Madinah"},{"b":"6.0","c":"لَيُخْرِجَنَّ","d":"layukh'rijanna","e":"surely will expel"},{"b":"8.1","c":"الْأَعَزُّ","d":"l-aʿazu","e":"the more honorable"},{"b":"9.2","c":"مِنْهَا","d":"min'hā","e":"from it"},{"b":"9.8","c":"الْأَذَلَّ","d":"l-adhala","e":"the more humble"},{"b":"11.2","c":"وَلِلَّهِ","d":"walillahi","e":"But for Allah"},{"b":"12.4","c":"الْعِزَّةُ","d":"l-ʿizatu","e":"(is) the honor"},{"b":"13.5","c":"وَلِرَسُولِهِ","d":"walirasūlihi","e":"and for His Messenger"},{"b":"15.0","c":"وَلِلْمُؤْمِنِينَ","d":"walil'mu'minīna","e":"and for the believers"},{"b":"16.8","c":"وَلَكِنَّ","d":"walākinna","e":"but"},{"b":"18.6","c":"الْمُنَافِقِينَ","d":"l-munāfiqīna","e":"the hypocrites"},{"b":"20.","c":"لَا","d":"lā","e":"(do) not"},{"b":"20.6","c":"يَعْلَمُونَ","d":"yaʿlamūna","e":"know"}],"a":{"g":"They say, \"If we return to al-Madinah, the more honored [for power] will surely expel therefrom the more humble.\" And to Allah belongs [all] honor, and to His Messenger, and to the believers, but the hypocrites do not know."}},"9":{"w":[{"b":"0.07","c":"يَاأَيُّهَا","d":"yāayyuhā","e":"O"},{"b":"3.0","c":"الَّذِينَ","d":"alladhīna","e":"you (who)"},{"b":"4.0","c":"ءَامَنُوا","d":"āmanū","e":"believe"},{"b":"5.0","c":"لَا","d":"lā","e":"(Let) not"},{"b":"5.4","c":"تُلْهِكُمْ","d":"tul'hikum","e":"divert you"},{"b":"6.4","c":"أَمْوَالُكُمْ","d":"amwālukum","e":"your wealth"},{"b":"7.8","c":"وَلَا","d":"walā","e":"and not"},{"b":"8.1","c":"أَوْلَادُكُمْ","d":"awlādukum","e":"your children"},{"b":"11.2","c":"عَنْ","d":"ʿan","e":"from"},{"b":"12.4","c":"ذِكْرِ","d":"dhik'ri","e":"(the) remembrance"},{"b":"13.0","c":"اللَّهِ","d":"l-lahi","e":"(of) Allah"},{"b":"15.8","c":"وَمَنْ","d":"waman","e":"And whoever"},{"b":"17.","c":"يَفْعَلْ","d":"yafʿal","e":"does"},{"b":"17.9","c":"ذَلِكَ","d":"dhālika","e":"that"},{"b":"18.7","c":"فَأُولَئِكَ","d":"fa-ulāika","e":"then those"},{"b":"21.5","c":"هُمُ","d":"humu","e":"[they]"},{"b":"21.9","c":"الْخَاسِرُونَ","d":"l-khāsirūna","e":"(are) the losers"}],"a":{"g":"O you who have believed, let not your wealth and your children divert you from remembrance of Allah. And whoever does that - then those are the losers."}},"10":{"w":[{"b":"0.04","c":"وَأَنْفِقُوا","d":"wa-anfiqū","e":"And spend"},{"b":"1.9","c":"مِنْ","d":"min","e":"from"},{"b":"3.1","c":"مَا","d":"mā","e":"what"},{"b":"3.3","c":"رَزَقْنَاكُمْ","d":"razaqnākum","e":"We have provided you"},{"b":"5.7","c":"مِنْ","d":"min","e":"from"},{"b":"6.9","c":"قَبْلِ","d":"qabli","e":"before"},{"b":"7.6","c":"أَنْ","d":"an","e":"[that]"},{"b":"8.6","c":"يَأْتِيَ","d":"yatiya","e":"comes"},{"b":"9.3","c":"أَحَدَكُمُ","d":"aḥadakumu","e":"(to) one of you"},{"b":"10.3","c":"الْمَوْتُ","d":"l-mawtu","e":"the death"},{"b":"11.1","c":"فَيَقُولَ","d":"fayaqūla","e":"and he says"},{"b":"15.8","c":"رَبِّ","d":"rabbi","e":"My Lord"},{"b":"16.4","c":"لَوْلَا","d":"lawlā","e":"Why not"},{"b":"18.6","c":"أَخَّرْتَنِي","d":"akhartanī","e":"You delay me"},{"b":"21.3","c":"إِلَى","d":"ilā","e":"for"},{"b":"22.2","c":"أَجَلٍ","d":"ajalin","e":"a term"},{"b":"24.7","c":"قَرِيبٍ","d":"qarībin","e":"near"},{"b":"26.3","c":"فَأَصَّدَّقَ","d":"fa-aṣṣaddaqa","e":"so I would give charity"},{"b":"27.7","c":"وَأَكُنْ","d":"wa-akun","e":"and be"},{"b":"29.4","c":"مِنَ","d":"mina","e":"among"},{"b":"29.6","c":"الصَّالِحِينَ","d":"l-ṣāliḥīna","e":"the righteous"}],"a":{"g":"And spend [in the way of Allah] from what We have provided you before death approaches one of you and he says, \"My Lord, if only You would delay me for a brief term so I would give charity and be among the righteous.\""}},"11":{"w":[{"b":"0.05","c":"وَلَنْ","d":"walan","e":"But never"},{"b":"1.2","c":"يُؤَخِّرَ","d":"yu-akhira","e":"will (be) delayed"},{"b":"2.1","c":"اللَّهُ","d":"l-lahu","e":"(by) Allah"},{"b":"2.9","c":"نَفْسًا","d":"nafsan","e":"a soul"},{"b":"3.6","c":"إِذَا","d":"idhā","e":"when"},{"b":"4.2","c":"جَاءَ","d":"jāa","e":"has come"},{"b":"6.8","c":"أَجَلُهَا","d":"ajaluhā","e":"its term"},{"b":"8.5","c":"وَاللَّهُ","d":"wal-lahu","e":"And Allah"},{"b":"9.4","c":"خَبِيرٌ","d":"khabīrun","e":"(is) All-Aware"},{"b":"11.0","c":"بِمَا","d":"bimā","e":"of what"},{"b":"11.7","c":"تَعْمَلُونَ","d":"taʿmalūna","e":"you do"}],"a":{"g":"But never will Allah delay a soul when its time has come. And Allah is Acquainted with what you do."}}}